  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "武将たちが活発に動き出す！戦国時代を描いた名作がパワーアップ！独自の武将を駆使して、世界統一の夢を実現するために戦略と戦術を尽くそう！シナリオは2つあり、約400人の実在の武将が登場。さらに、野戦と包囲戦モードも搭載されており、汗をかくような戦闘のスリルを楽しむことができる。今こそ、意思の中で散らばる大名・織田信長の大志を果たす時だ！",
      "lang": "ja",
      "source": "romu"
    },
    {
      "text": "The warlords start moving lively! A masterpiece depicting the Sengoku period is powered up! Now is the time to fulfill the great ambitions of Nobunaga Oda, who has been scattered in the midst of his ambitions by making full use of his unique warlords and doing his best in strategy and tactics! \"Nobunaga's Ambition: Sengoku Gunyuden\" is now available on Game Boy! !! The scenario is equipped with two episodes, \"Gunyu Wari\" in 1560 and \"Nobunaga's Ambition\" in 1582. There are more than 400 warlords. Equipped with \"field battle\" and \"siege battle\" modes.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    }
  ],
